Payment terms have changed:
Minor changes to the payment terms included in the Purchase Order terms and conditions;

Purchase Orders terms and conditions dated before 15 December 2017: Sixty (60) calendar days or in the next semi-monthly payment run thereafter.

Purchase Orders dated on or after 15 December 2017: The later of sixty (60) calendar days or the next processing run immediately thereafter.
